    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>走进内心。整理思绪。放松下来。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704840/extras/c173c2c0f0d10e4c1889faa5d7353e24.avif?t=1770683654\" width=780 height=208 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PsyUp 是一款极简风格的物理解谜游戏，带有心理氛围 ——  <br>每一次打碎方块，都像是在卸下心中的负担。<br><br>没有戏剧化的表达，也没有复杂的说教。  <br>只有那种把内在混乱重新整理好的舒适感。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>打碎方块，从未如此令人满足</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704840/extras/c002e77df4fb7b2b1215dd17c7af2cb4.poster.avif?t=1770683654\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704840/extras/c002e77df4fb7b2b1215dd17c7af2cb4.webm?t=1770683654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704840/extras/c002e77df4fb7b2b1215dd17c7af2cb4.mp4?t=1770683654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>点击。破坏。释放。重组。</strong></h2><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><br>每一个动作都在瓦解内心的紧张，  <br>就像是在整理自己的思绪 ——  <br>一种简单，却强大的仪式。</i></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>上手简单，感受深刻。</strong></p><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关卡简短</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >即时反馈</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让人忍不住“再来一关”的感觉</p></li></ul><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><br>挑战物理规则，放松你的大脑，  <br>在一块一块的拆解中，感受秩序回归混乱之上。</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>一段穿越人类心智的旅程</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704840/extras/ece4a880652f6216f10b741e9cbad802.avif?t=1770683654\" width=776 height=238 /></span><br><strong>灵感来自心理现象的关卡设计</strong></h2><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个世界都有属于自己的 <strong>“性格”</strong>：  <br>像焦虑一样迅速，像多动症一样混乱，  <br>又或像完美主义一样严谨。<br><br><strong>将真实的人类情绪，转化为物理解谜体验。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为放松而生</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704840/extras/b85f135c6a9ace7e47258ac8fa96ea19.poster.avif?t=1770683654\" width=780 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704840/extras/b85f135c6a9ace7e47258ac8fa96ea19.webm?t=1770683654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704840/extras/b85f135c6a9ace7e47258ac8fa96ea19.mp4?t=1770683654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>柔和的声音、平缓的节奏与干净的视觉设计</strong>  <br>营造出一个让大脑慢慢放松的空间。<br><br>PsyUp 被设计成日常中的短暂休息 ——  <br><strong>一次轻松、舒服的情绪呼吸。</strong><br><br>画面不拥挤，没有催促。  <br><strong>只有你、方块，以及随着一切归位而出现的平静。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为什么要玩？</strong></h2><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704840/extras/58319ab3ca95ce191d862bbb195f4e7f.avif?t=1770683654\" width=780 height=208 /></span><br><br><strong>★ 沉浸式心理氛围</strong>  <br><i>— 每个世界都拥有独特的情绪基调。</i><br><br><strong>★ 简单却上瘾的物理解谜</strong>  <br>— 点击、破坏、发现规律，进入心流状态。<br><br><strong>★ 令人难忘的主题世界</strong>  <br>— 每个关卡都探索人类心智的一部分。<br><br><strong>★ 真正的减压体验</strong>  <br>— 打碎方块，从未如此解压。<br><br><strong>★ 为放松而设计的音画体验</strong>  <br>— 柔和、干净，令人愉悦。</p>",
